# Nexus 工程规范

## Monorepo 目录（`packages/` 优先）

```
nexus/
├── packages/
│   ├── kernel/          # L1 Harness：query-engine, compact, checkpoint, lifecycle, environment, oercd, state-graph
│   ├── control-plane/   # L2：run-manager, approval, policy, budget, orchestration, context-policy, model-router, retry-policy, sunset-engine
│   ├── tool-gateway/    # build-tool, result-budget, protocol-adapters
│   ├── memory/          # session-shadow, episodic, skill-store, federation-guard
│   ├── guardrails/
│   ├── providers/       # prompt-assembler, prompt-cache(stable-prefix/cache-aware-compact)
│   ├── observability/   # traces, metrics, decision-chain, cognitive-heatmap, explainability-api
│   ├── shared/          # types, errors, events (S0)
│   ├── phase-intent/    # L3 Phase 1 能力包（意图层）
│   ├── phase-execution/ # L3 Phase 2 能力包（执行层）
│   ├── phase-connection/# L3 Phase 3 能力包（连接层）
│   └── infra/           # 基础设施胶水
├── apps/
│   ├── api-gateway/     # HTTP/WS 网关
│   ├── console/         # 管理控制台
│   └── cli/
├── mcp-servers/         # MCP Server 独立进程（pm-tools, dev-tools, feishu, dingtalk, oa）
├── compensation/        # L4 必须有 sunsetDate
└── evals/
```

> Phase 能力包（L3）在 `packages/phase-*` 下，**不是**根目录 `capability-packs/`。`compensation/`（L4）在根目录。

## TypeScript

1. `strict: true`；公共 API 用 `interface`
2. 联合类型 / `const enum` 优于运行时 enum
3. `async/await`；`readonly` / `Readonly<T>` 优先
4. 公共契约标注 `@stability S0|S1|…`（JSDoc）

## 错误体系（`packages/shared/errors`）

> 基类名为 `NexusError`（v3.0），不是 `AgentError`。

```typescript
/** Nexus 领域错误基类 */
class NexusError extends Error {
  constructor(
    message: string,
    readonly code: string,         // 格式：DOMAIN.SUB_CODE
    readonly retryable: boolean = false,
    readonly context?: Readonly<Record<string, unknown>>,
    options?: ErrorOptions,
  ) {
    super(message, options);
    this.name = this.constructor.name;
  }
}

class ToolExecutionError   extends NexusError {}
class ProviderError        extends NexusError {}
class GuardrailViolation   extends NexusError {}
class OrchestrationError   extends NexusError {}
class BudgetExhaustedError extends NexusError {}
class ApprovalTimeoutError extends NexusError {}
class CheckpointCorruptionError extends NexusError {}
class PackLoadError        extends NexusError {}
class RetrievalError       extends NexusError {}
```

## Prompt

- 模板与逻辑 **分离**（`prompts.ts` / `providers/prompt-assembler.ts`）
- System Prompt **六层**（Layer 1–4 = `stable_prefix`；Layer 5–6 = `dynamic_suffix`）详见 §17.5
- 外部内容必须隔离（§17.7）；禁止日志打印完整 Prompt

## 配置

- 环境变量 → 启动时 Zod 校验的 config 对象；**fail-fast**
- 密钥走 Secret Manager，禁止入库/入日志

## 测试

| 层级 | 范围 | 工具 |
|------|------|------|
| 单元 | 工具、Compact、护栏 | Vitest |
| 集成 | AgentRun 端到端 | Mock LLM + 录制回放 |
| 评估 | 任务成功率、韧性指标 | `evals/` |
